{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#11022: style vars doesn't work with wrapped teleport",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:22:44.942256+00:00",
  "text": "style vars doesn't work with wrapped teleport\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.4.27\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nPrevious issue has been fixed for the content in 'local' teleports, but when teleport is located inside another component, v-bind won't work. \r\n\r\nRepro portraits the problem perfectly\n\n### What is expected?\n\nStyles applied correctly\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nStyles does not apply\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":lady_beetle:  bug",
    "scope: teleport",
    ":hammer: p3-minor-bug"
  ],
